<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Transportation may change an adjustment or arrangement made under this chapter as the Secretary considers necessary to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6ef4228-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s8/c">Pub. L. 109–304, § 8(c)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1658">120 Stat. 1658</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
